        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### Activation\n\nBuilt-in Grafana panels + Infinity cannot reliably do authenticated JSON POST with body templating for each row.\n\nUse one of these plugins for click-to-activate:\n\n1. Volkov Labs Business Forms\n2. Volkov Labs Data Manipulation\n\nPOST URL: `${control_url}/control/activate`\n\nHeaders:\n\n- `Authorization: Bearer ${control_token}`\n- `Content-Type: application/json`\n\nBody:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"group\": \"core\",\n  \"uplink\": \"uplink-02\",\n  \"transport\": \"tcp\"\n}\n```\n\nLegacy compatibility endpoint also exists: `POST /switch?group=...&uplink=...&transport=tcp|udp|both`.\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Activate uplink",
      "type": "text"
